@startuml
title Ingest 处理执行用例图（当前实现 + 规划）

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "客户端/前端" as Client
actor "处理 Worker" as Worker
actor "运维/开发者" as Ops

rectangle "Ingest Processing Execution" {
  usecase "轮询并抢占待处理文档\nUPLOADED -> INGESTING (CAS)" as UC_Claim
  usecase "执行文档处理\n读取源文件 -> 解析 -> 分块 -> 向量写入" as UC_Process
  usecase "处理状态收口\nINGESTING -> INDEXED/FAILED (CAS)" as UC_Close
  usecase "查询文档状态\nGET /documents/{id}/status" as UC_Status
  usecase "查询分块预览\nGET /documents/{id}/chunks/preview" as UC_Preview
  usecase "失败重试（草案）\n指数退避 + jitter" as UC_Retry
  usecase "人工重处理（草案）\nPOST /documents/{id}/reprocess" as UC_Reprocess
}

Worker --> UC_Claim
Worker --> UC_Process
Worker --> UC_Close
Client --> UC_Status
Client --> UC_Preview
Ops --> UC_Reprocess

UC_Process .> UC_Close : <<include>>
UC_Retry ..> UC_Process : <<extend>>
UC_Reprocess ..> UC_Claim : <<extend>>

note right of UC_Process
当前实现已落地：
- Tika 解析 + 文本清洗
- 结构优先 + 长度兜底分块
- PGVector 向量写入（delete + add 幂等）
end note

@enduml
